rush show - Show package files.

[1mUsage:[0m
  rush show PACKAGE [FILE]
  rush show --help | -h

[1mOptions:[0m
  [32m--help, -h[0m
    Show this help

[1mArguments:[0m
  [32mPACKAGE[0m
    Package name.
    
    This can either be the package name without the repository name (in this
    case, the default repository will be used) or in the form of `repo:package`.

  [32mFILE[0m
    File to show (show all if not specified).

[1mExamples:[0m
  rush show docker
  rush show docker main
